      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a bad day though. it's everything. i just look at them and i can feel how much my mess is affecting them. like, if i wasn't even around, they could actually have a chance at a real, happy life. wouldn't it be more selfless to just... stop being a burden to them?",
