      "role": "user",
      "content": "but they're constantly looking at me with such sadness. i see it in their eyes. it's like they're constantly trying to pick up the pieces of me. wouldn't it be easier for them to just start over with someone who isn't so broken? like, why is it always considered \"good\" to stay when staying just makes everything worse for the people you love?",
